{"tid":1306774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔「連儂牆」岌岌可危","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:48:03.000Z","uid":38080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"288ff92cc23c5ac44e3a71fc2cac6d870fedffc2","tid":1306774,"uid":38080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】7月12日清理佔用隧道欄杆及土地 大埔「連儂牆」岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n大埔港鐵站行人隧道變身「連儂牆」，牆身貼滿貼紙。7月7日旺角清場撩示威者「隻揪」、綽號「香焦糖」的警員被網民起底，包括他的個人資料、相片及學校資料等30張標貼，貼在「連儂牆」。警方勞師動眾，昨凌晨出動60名防暴警，在大埔「連儂牆」清理該些標貼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然警方今次行動沒有針對市民的標貼，但大埔「連儂牆」仍岌岌可危，大埔地政處在隧道張貼通告，任何人士在7月12日停止佔用隧道欄杆及附近土地，當日有聯合行動，清理及充公停泊該處的單車，亦有可能一併將「連儂牆」清理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpyJ2kV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpyJ2kV.jpg&h=c915271e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0335a2fb1790cef3b8a9de70a93e8ec556615e78","tid":1306774,"uid":207462,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"拆完再起冇問題<br />\n大埔又唔係得一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372a6386df9e28ca7c4c37d573ea7c6f0d8016ca","tid":1306774,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"cf2ef3e27016a11218f3a01f81ac7ffb43f379eb","tid":1306774,"uid":71237,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"[策略] 連儂牆宜貼不宜守<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304314\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304314</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29a35fec9fdd3508b9541332e9dc0cc3782e91ca","tid":1306774,"uid":211461,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"敵清我退 敵退我貼"},{"pid":"1cf9217c2b08a14e75fd3079b66276473b6b099e","tid":1306774,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n<br />\n一日復活"},{"pid":"41a65ea21888a596541ec0839b2277b107b8b41c","tid":1306774,"uid":15